  "2026-06-07T12:58:08.908Z",codex-active-pm-cycle-20260607,"External dependency fix implemented in pm-changelog repo under tracking item pmc-ph6q on branch fix/classifier-remove-command-name-routing: classifier now treats Removed as strong-signal first and evaluates weak title-only remove/delete after Added/Changed defaults to avoid remove-type/create_default_type misrouting. Added regressions in pm-changelog/test/generator.test.ts and verified via npm run build && npm test && npm run check && npm run changelog:check in pm-changelog. Local pm-cli validation with latest published pm-changelog: pnpm changelog:pm:check pass (installed pm-changelog@2026.6.7)."
