body: "## Context\\nclassifyItem in the separate pm-changelog repo (src/generator.ts) checks Removed via hasAny(allValues, [removed,remove,deleted,delete]) which runs before the strong-tier Changed needles and the bug-like-type default. allValues includes the sanitized title; the sanitizer strips --flags but not plain hyphenated words.\\n\\n## Evidence\\n- pm-changelog src/generator.ts (Removed rule ordering + hasAny word-boundary match)\\n- Live repro: closing pm-z5nb ('...remove-type, add-status...') produced a '### Removed' changelog line for a plan that removed nothing (reverted in this PR by reopening pm-z5nb)\\n\\n## Acceptance criteria\\n- See structured acceptance_criteria field."
